verbose_text: This study observed the effects of ramipril (RAM) on the expression changes of IGF-1, fibronectin (FN), type IV collagen (Col-IV), and matrix metalloproteinases (MMP) -2 in STZ induced DN rats, hoping to explore the possible mechanism of ACEI in treating DN.
